General.Name: Move About Group AB
General.Description: Move About Group AB (publ) provides app-based mobility solutions to individuals, companies, municipalities, and organizations in Sweden, Norway, and Germany. The company's platform gives digital access to electric cars, electric bicycles, taxi, subway, and parking. It offers subscription-based pay-per-use service serving approximately 70,000 subscribers have access to approximately 700 electric cars for their short city trip, business trip, or weekend enjoyment. The company was founded in 2007 and is based in Gothenburg, Sweden.
